.DT
set_wield_func
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_wield_func

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_wield_func -  This method sets the wield function of the object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_wield_func(string func,
mixed ob)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^func%^RESET%^ - the function to call
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object to call the method on

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/weapon.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the wield function of the object.  This will be
called when the object is wielded and unwielded.
.EP

